{"tid":2379604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(即時傳譯 + 討論)德國國會將會喺香港時間7點鐘就制裁中國開聽證會","createTime":"2021-01-25T10:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T11:27:44.000Z","uid":84325,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4591418996f4b61b0887a4861cbe7740f43ec920","tid":2379604,"uid":84325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">大家記唔記得曾經簽過一份德文嘅petition?</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2020/_07/_02/Petition_113264.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2020%2F_07%2F_02%2FPetition_113264.nc.html&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=7b12fff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2020/_07/_02/Petition_113264.nc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n内容列出九項訴求，包括要求德國政府制裁打壓香港人嘅官員，要求德國喺聯合國提出派人調查香港警暴個案，要求德國政府取消一年一度嘅歐中峰會等等。<br />\n<br />\n多得各位連登仔擁躍支持，鄺頌晴將會同曾經留學中國，被中國政府驅逐出境嘅activist David Missal 一齊喺德國國會回應政府同議員嘅提問。最終，委員會將會決定是否將呢項議案交上大會討論。<br />\n<br />\n直播將會喺德國時間12點正開始。Link 喺呢度: <a href=\"http://bundestag.de\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbundestag.de&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=8e2c22b3\" target=\"_blank\">bundestag.de</a>"},{"pid":"830f3ea6132188bdd7eb7e57a1160f40505e8640","tid":2379604,"uid":84325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T10:33:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">唔好唔記得follow埋德國戰線嘅朋友: <br />\nWir f&uuml;r Hongkong: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/w4hongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fw4hongkong&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=f0caf30f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/w4hongkong</a><br />\n香港人在德國協會: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HongkongerV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHongkongerV&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQA